{"tid":165210,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[官字兩個口]選舉事務處:候選人擁歐居留權未能確立","createTime":"2017-03-21T07:56:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-21T11:20:04.000Z","uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cb0d8a6c5f6c3d253410b2a11051c6cdfd781f76","tid":165210,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T07:56:53.000Z","msg":"有報道質疑有行政長官選舉候選人的家庭成員有歐盟居留權，因而本身也有歐盟的居留權，以致不符合參選資格，選舉事務處發言人回應稱，選舉主任經徵詢<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>律政司</strong></span>法律意見後，就有關候選人<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>擁有外國居留權；虛報沒有外國居留權；以及參加行政長官選舉的資格應予以取消的指稱，未能得以確立。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n選舉事務處表示，換言之，選舉主任於3月7日刊載憲報所公布的3名行政長官選舉候選人，為<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>獲有效提名的決定沒有改變</strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥日前接受訪問時透露，自己與家人在回歸前透過居英權計劃取得英國國籍，她在2007年上任發展局局長前已放棄，但丈夫林兆波及兩名兒子就一直持英籍至今，並表明即使她當選都無意放棄。"},{"pid":"b91190649405df5fc2228f2d1e4355a0e84307f8","tid":165210,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T07:58:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/1518635/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F1518635%2F&d=0ZNtUZ9Qk1f13jNJdsSeNxv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=45982f17\" target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/1518635/</a><br />\n<br />\n補Link"},{"pid":"1450d5dd6e214e6844cf522ad0b384555b0527d5","tid":165210,"uid":7840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T07:59:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6404ebf166f7ce256055082ff13af5592ad8a615","tid":165210,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T08:00:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Why<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n應該係未實際擁有？強國猿D理論我地凡人睇唔透的"},{"pid":"3a766757522847a861e37f124ab78382eb52fe9a","tid":165210,"uid":2923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T08:03:49.000Z","msg":"未能確立,咁又唔解